{"documents": ["Standard delivery takes 3 to 5 working days. Same-day delivery is available only in selected cities. If an order is delayed beyond the promised date, the customer can request a support ticket or callback.", "Customers can track orders using their order ID. For payment failures, customers should wait 30 minutes and check whether money was refunded automatically. For urgent support, customers can request human escalation.", "Customers can request a refund within 7 days of delivery if the product is unused, undamaged, and returned with original invoice and packaging. Refunds are processed within 3 to 5 working days after quality inspection.", "Most electronics include a 1-year limited warranty covering manufacturing defects. Physical damage, water damage, and unauthorized repair are not covered under warranty."], "metadatas": [{"source": "delivery_policy.txt"}, {"source": "faq.txt"}, {"source": "refund_policy.txt"}, {"source": "warranty_policy.txt"}], "embeddings": [[0.003231910988688469, -0.05090738832950592, 0.09209933876991272, 0.022989574819803238, -0.03159051015973091, -0.09277503192424774, -0.10779524594545364, -0.06760405749082565, -0.030643314123153687, 0.03803035616874695, 0.08020513504743576, 0.023485057055950165, -0.009614727459847927, -0.011009893380105495, 0.05500221252441406, -0.03543912246823311, 0.04256707802414894, -0.10839059203863144, -0.08858881890773773, 0.05973513051867485, -0.01163223385810852, -0.011376769281923771, -0.06857165694236755, -0.004783743992447853, 0.001651971135288477, -0.012992867268621922, -0.05154397711157799, 0.009218484163284302, 0.015027089044451714, -0.055666401982307434, -0.02383027784526348, -0.012134077958762646, 0.0005367895937524736, 0.02927883341908455, 0.006304447073489428, 0.00680180499330163, -0.009556487202644348, -0.0454406701028347, 0.04322891682386398, -0.004009703174233437, 0.03400326147675514, 0.06478339433670044, -0.027159713208675385, 0.06819901615381241, -0.03600778430700302, -0.0267966501414